OL,6,FCumberland Council says that its
OL,7,Fbudget for the next financial year
OL,8,F"protects front-line services" as
OL,9,Fcouncil tax is set to rise by nearly
OL,10,Ffive per cent.
OL,12,FThe latest budget was agreed at a
OL,13,Fcouncil meeting in on Wednesday 6
OL,14,FMarch.
OL,16,FIt will see the levy increase by 4.99%
OL,17,Fin the Cumberland area with the
OL,18,Fpremium on second homes set to
OL,19,Fincrease by 100%.
