OL,4,Cfive per cent as council agrees budget
OL,6,FPayments for council tax will double
OL,7,Ffor second home owners in the
OL,8,FCumberland area from 2025/26. This
OL,9,Ffollows on from a survey conducted by
OL,10,Fthe council which found that over 70%
OL,11,Fof people that took part believed
OL,12,Fcouncil tax should double for second
OL,13,Fhome owners.
OL,15,FSpeaking on the budget, Councillor
OL,16,FBarbara Cannon, Executive member with
OL,17,Fresponsibility for financial planning
OL,18,Fand assets, said: "I'm pleased that
OL,19,Fcouncillors have agreed our budget for
OL,20,Fthe next financial year.
