OL,3,CCouncil Tax set to increase by almost
OL,4,Cfive per cent as council agrees budget
OL,6,F"The budget not only provides the
OL,7,Ffunding needed to continue with our
OL,8,Ffrontline services that so many people
OL,9,Frely on, but it also means that we can
OL,10,Fdeliver on the priorities of the
OL,11,Fpeople of Cumberland.
OL,13,F"As has been the situation for
OL,14,Fcouncils up and down the country,
OL,15,Fsetting this budget has brought its
OL,16,Fchallenges. Local government funding
OL,17,Fhas been severely stretched in recent
OL,18,Fyears at a time when demand for
OL,19,Fservices has been rising fast.
