OL,3,CCouncil Tax set to increase by almost
OL,4,Cfive per cent as council agrees budget
OL,6,F"The responsibilities of local
OL,7,Fgovernment have grown too with many of
OL,8,Four residents not realising the full
OL,9,Fbreadth of services we provide from
OL,10,Fsocial care to leisure centres,
OL,11,Fplanning, highways and public health.
OL,13,F"This is why our transformation plan
OL,14,Fis so important, not only to make our
OL,15,Fservices more effective, but also to
OL,16,Fput us on a more stable financial
OL,17,Ffooting in the future.
