OL,6,F"We have a plan and we need to stick
OL,7,Fto it to achieve the improvements to
OL,8,Fservices we want to see for our
OL,9,Fresidents, and realise the
OL,10,Fopportunities of local government
OL,11,Freorganisation."
OL,13,Fhas also included funding for the
OL,14,Fcouncil tax reduction scheme which is
OL,15,Ftargeted to support people on low
OL,16,Fincomes.
