OL,6,FThe council say that they will be
OL,7,Ffocusing their spending on improving
OL,8,Fthe health and wellbeing of residents.
OL,9,FOver the next 12 months anti-smoking
OL,10,Fcampaigns and live longer better
OL,11,Fcampaigns will be rolled out.
OL,13,FThe council also say they are going to
OL,14,Fincrease the amount of electric
OL,15,Fvehicle charging points in the area.
OL,17,FThe budget is said to protect public
OL,18,Fservices including schools, libraries
OL,19,Fand roads.
