OL,6,FCouncillor Barbara Cannon added:
OL,7,F"Putting up council tax is never an
OL,8,Feasy decision especially at a time
OL,9,Fwhen people's own budgets are
OL,10,Fstretched.
OL,12,F"With costs rising, increasing council
OL,13,Ftax helps protect services that are so
OL,14,Fimportant for many of our residents -
OL,15,Fa situation which residents understand
OL,16,Fgiven their responses to our
OL,17,Fconsultation.
