OL,3,CCouncil Tax set to increase by almost
OL,4,Cfive per cent as council agrees budget
OL,6,F"For those on the lowest incomes, we
OL,7,Fhave one of the most generous council
OL,8,Ftax reduction schemes in the country,
OL,9,Fand I'd encourage anyone who is
OL,10,Fstruggling to pay their bill to
OL,11,Fcontact our customer service team to
OL,12,Fdiscuss whether they are eligible for
OL,13,Fthis support.
OL,15,F"The additional income from second
OL,16,Fhomes will help us address the housing
OL,17,Fissues many of our communities face as
OL,18,Fwell as help bring these homes back
OL,19,Finto full-time use."
